          <text>
                    <body>
                              <pb n="1"/>
                              <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Charleston, S. C.</placeName>
                                        <date>April 8. 1853</date>.</p>
                              <p><addressee>Rev. I. Leeser</addressee>,
                                                  <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>.</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">Dear Sir! Will you be pleased to<lb/> send me
                                        regularly the Occident and forward your bill<lb/> to your
                                        agent in this city. (beginning with No 1 of Vol. XI.)</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">A friend of mine presented me this week<lb/> with
                                        a series of the Occident, complete, with the exception<lb/>
                                        of the 6<hi rend="sup">th</hi> vol. the 1<hi rend="sup"
                                                  >st</hi> number of which is lost. You would<lb/>
                                        therefore confer a great favor upon me, if you could
                                        send<lb/> me, by mail, this No 1 of Vol. VI as I am
                                        very<lb/> anxious to have my series of the O. complete.</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">I embrace this opportunity, to inform you,<lb/> as
                                        an old friend, of my being engaged to be married to<lb/>
                                        <persName>Miss Rachel Ottolengui</persName>, daughter of the
                                        late <persName>Abraham<lb/> Ottolengui</persName> of this
                                        city.</p>
                              <p rend="indent(8)">I remain with my best regards</p>
                              <p rend="indent(8)">Yours</p>
                              <p rend="indent(9)">most respectfully</p>
                              <p rend="indent(10)">
                                        <persName role="author">Dr M Mayer</persName>
                              </p>
                              <pb n="2"/>
                              <p><addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee>,</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">
                                        <placeName>371 Walnut St.</placeName>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(2)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>.</p>
